| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4840 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 308dae1d-6b44-586d-906c-9913d9b7c7e4"
